<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title">Elliott Takes 11% stake in F&#038;C <span class="divider">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span></span><!-- end .title --> The hedge fund Elliott Management disclosed an 11 percent stake in the British asset manager F&#038;C, worth about Â£80 million, The Financial Times writes. Analysts expect Elliott to use its stake to attract new bidders and push for a higher sale price.<br /><span class="elsewhere"><a href="//www.ft.com/intl/cms/s/0/ae1bb65c-9f03-11e3-8663-00144feab7de.html#axzz2uBlgoJ8U"> FINANCIAL TIMES </a></span></p>
